snippet.title: Lethal League Blaze Trailer
snippet.description:
Get the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/553310/Lethal_League_Blaze/

The game is coming to Nintendo Switch, Playstation 4 and Xbox One in Spring 2019

Music: 
Hideki Naganuma - Ain't nothing like a funky beat
